Cinnamon Toast Crunch's newest marketing campaign surrounds a sinister square on a terrifying murder spree. While Cinnamon Toast Crunch squares have always been cannibals, these new commercials turn the dial up to 11 and emphasize the horror aspect. Is this an effective marketing campaign?
